title: 2 Bottom, no Jungle
body: Not a big deal, but did a game of flex today and we had two Bottoms and no Jungle

replies.body: This usually happens in 5 mans where more than one player has queued up as a role. It can also sometimes happen in 3s and 4s when players have switched positions (one has mid/top, the other has top/mid). It only ever happens in premades where there is an expectation of communication, and only occurs with roles that have been actively selected.
Ah yes. That was our situation: 5 man, all in comms.
